    {"type":"text","id":"layer3b","x":106,"y":592,"width":844,"height":52,"text":"Tension packet spec · processing protocol · workspace architecture · memory continuity\nMetabolic override protocol · trigger sensing · governed agent constellation pattern\nOpen reference patterns that show how the constitution actually runs","fontSize":16,"fontFamily":2,"strokeColor":"#495057"},

